{"title": "That Was the Reward", "content": "A character refuses something that is offered to him or may even destroy said thing. Afterwards, he learns that the item was his reward for a recent task he successfully or exceptionally completed. In some cases, the spurned/destroyed item was meant as a gift (e.g. birthday, wedding, Valentine's Day).\n\nUsually meant as An Aesop or could also be Laser-Guided Karma if the character in question is a Jerkass or arrogant. Also may be Played for Laughs.\n\nMay overlap with My New Gift Is Lame and Vandalism Backfire. Compare Undesirable Prize, which the character knows is meant for them but may actually be tempted to refuse or destroy, and Off the Table, when there's an attempt to claim the gift but it will not be given after the initial refusal.", "url": "https://tvtropes.org/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/ThatWasTheReward", "media_links": ["/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Anime/BurnUp", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/LaurelAndHardy", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Film/TheMusicBox", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Film/TheDayTheEarthStoodStill1951", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Film/TheThreeStooges", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/HGWells", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Creator/RudyardKipling", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/HarryPotterAndTheGobletOfFire", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Literature/MissMarple", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Series/LoisAndClark", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Series/TheTwilightZone", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Series/MamasFamily", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Series/Victorious", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Series/Cheers", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Series/DennisTheMenace", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/TheRaccoons", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/LooneyTunes", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/WesternAnimation/DonaldDuck"], "non_media_links": ["/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/MacGuffin", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/AnAesop", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/LaserGuidedKarma", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/Jerkass", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/SmallNameBigEgo", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/PlayedForLaughs", "/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/MyNewGiftIsLame", "/pm